include ../../media-object/media-object
include ../../avatar/avatar

p "Media object" module helper for easily creating blocks with text and image, like comments, any lists and etc.

h4 Example usage in `comment` module
style
	:stylus
		.comment
			&__avatar
				//
			&__text
				margin 0 10px
			&__message
				font-size 14px
				line-height 20px
				margin-bottom 10px

			&__meta
				font-size 13px

			&__name
				&
				&:visited
					font-weight bold
					display inline-block
					margin-right 5px
					color #000
					text-decoration none

			&__date
				display inline-block
				color silver

h5 Top
.comment.media-object.media-object_image_top
	.comment__avatar.media-object__image
		+avatar({"image": "https://unsplash.it/240/240?image=1027", "title": "User Name"}).avatar_style_circle.avatar_size_small
	.comment__text.media-object__body
		.comment__meta
			a(href="#").comment__name User Name
			time(datetime="2017-12-20 08:30:45").comment__date 1 day ago
		.comment__message Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Perspiciatis, temporibus quam iste totam nam natus debitis quae, rem nulla, culpa delectus. Nam ex iusto repellat et fuga ullam omnis velit!
		.comment__controls
			button(type="button").button.button_style_ghost.button_color_blue.button_size_small Reply
			button(type="button").button.button_style_ghost.button_color_blue.button_size_small Quote
